short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: We are the future - connectivity in our veins. We are weitsicht

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Project weitsicht, which means foresight, is an online platform that allows digital citizens to share insights on their internet browsing routine.

We are concerned with default settings, security literacy and the future of the web. We are here to seek clarity, we try to understand and take action.

Extension is aware of what‘s in the browser right now, but doesn‘t store any data. Weitsicht does respect people's privacy.
